description: Amazing west-side location close to Red Line Stops and West Broadway! Gut renovated in 2017, this open plan two-bed condo in Southie is turn-key with all the perks. The kitchen comes complete with breakfast bar, S/S appliances, white cabinetry, and granite counters, with microwave and dishwasher both recently replaced. Oversized living room and foyer allow flexibility for dining or office space with room for extra storage. Down the hall you'll find two generous sized bedrooms with ample closet space and beautiful tile bath. Exiting out your back door, discover the huge common deck - perfect for lounging on those sunny days - leading to a beautiful park with picnic tables and doggy waste station. One of the few condos in the building with direct deck access! Washer/dryer located in unit. Heat is forced hot-air, with potential to add central A/C. Come and see it before it's gone!
